{"tid":1672369,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"倘亂局持續 不如拆了迪士尼起樓？","createTime":"2019-10-24T05:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T06:07:12.000Z","uid":241764,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6b373affb956fc2088aeee3827db9cc948388c","tid":1672369,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:21:26.000Z","msg":"香港6月起開始反修例示威，至8月抗議暴力惡化，訪港旅客尤其內地遊客大減，而香港的零售業也備受打擊，同一時間，香港迪士尼的入場人數也見銳減。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，及至9月初開始，迪士尼股價便開始大幅跑輸美股標普指數接近8%，或許便和香港迪士尼業績轉差有關，如香港亂局不止，幾可肯定迪士尼將會勁蝕。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>昨天有基金界朋友便指出，如香港繼續亂下去而內地遊客止步香港，不如將香港迪士尼結束經營，並將有關地皮改為發展住宅，可能明日大嶼的填海計劃也不用填。</strong><br />\n<br />\n該基金朋友說其實香港迪士尼已有基建配套，更已連接機鐵，地皮可即拆即用，不用慢慢填海，而除了迪士尼，如香港局勢繼續惡化，海洋公園也可拆去興建住宅。<br />\n<br />\n之前也有測量界建議在香港的貨櫃碼頭上興建住宅，會不會有一天香港的轉口港地位進一步萎縮，甚至貨櫃碼頭也可剷平建住宅？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1571893499178&amp;issue=20191024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1571893499178%26issue%3D20191024&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoby9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=cf794deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1571893499178&amp;issue=20191024</a><br />\n<br />\n其實都好, 反正都唔係俾香港人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318cf3a96a3431b06f42dc5584a77a873e0bc69b","tid":1672369,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SUCK 1026長龍爆買日<br />\n18區爆買日目標黃店（一）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PiTw4ry.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPiTw4ry.png&h=6278c244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3r8AMEZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3r8AMEZ.png&h=1b78b7e5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"51524e849742460b8f33d51abe05723ad36b3486","tid":1672369,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoby9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=6ca3d2e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoby9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=f84b2e9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoby9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=c9460196\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoby9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=a35862f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"93379818331b44fd60477fbd439c83747481f3d2","tid":1672369,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"個迪士尼光復之後仲要架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ceb5ea5a180f025699987eee1aaad2d45d7ce8d","tid":1672369,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:41:57.000Z","msg":"起樓俾新香港人？"},{"pid":"ecff689107048d5bd2dd01a299abf93a207f2c95","tid":1672369,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"海洋公園好多香港人童年集體回憶"},{"pid":"75c46d0c9804a9e7c6bb1de6e87af6cf014a2ac6","tid":1672369,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"ok wo<br />\n拆迪迪尼咁可以變一堆高質中產樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 